name: AI
description: AI is an accessible package aimed at making Machine Learning & other branches of AI easier to build in Dynamo. Originally built for a lab session at the BiLT Europe 2017 conference, now expanded to include friendly concepts such as Machines. It currently uses the Accord.NET framework and has support for several algorithms such as regression, classifiers, clustering. See the repo for more info and tweet me @radugidei for any feedback or question.
